-- Billionaire Usmanov Plans to Boost Arsenal Football Club Stake
-- B y   Y u l i y a   F e d o r i n o v a
-- 2012-04-27T06:42:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-27/billionaire-usmanov-plans-to-boost-arsenal-football-club-stake.html
Russian billionaire  Alisher
Usmanov , who controls 30 percent of the Arsenal Football Club
with a business partner, will seek to boost the stake, according
to an interview broadcast on state television.  The soccer club is a “really good” business with strong
prospects, Usmanov said in an interview with the Rossiya 24
channel.  To contact the reporter on this story:
